@startuml 防御配置与效果评测时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantFontSize 13
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "DefenseCoordinator" as DC
participant "StrategyManager" as SM
participant "InputGuard" as IG
participant "RetrievalGuard" as RG
participant "OutputGuard" as OG

User -> Frontend : 提交查询请求
Frontend -> DC : process_query(query)
DC -> SM : get_active_strategy()
SM --> DC : 返回当前策略配置
DC -> IG : check_input(query)
IG -> IG : 提示注入检测与输入归一化
IG --> DC : 返回 GuardResult
DC -> RG : filter_evidence(candidates)
RG -> RG : 扩展检索、嵌入异常检测、PPL检测
RG --> DC : 返回过滤后证据
DC -> OG : verify_output(answer, evidence)
OG -> OG : 一致性校验与业务规则约束
OG --> DC : 返回 GuardResult
DC --> Frontend : 返回最终回答及防御结果
Frontend --> User : 展示回答及证据审查结果

@enduml
